      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " لَيْسَ يَبْقَى فِي الْجَوْفِ مِنْ غُدْوَةٍ إِلَى اللَّيْلِ إِلَّا خُبْزُ الْأَرُزِّ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Al Sayyari, from Yahya Bin Abu Rafi’a, and someone else, ",
          "(It has been narrated) raising it to Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Nothing from the early morning meal remains inside up to the night, except for the rice bread’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Muhammad ibn Yahya has narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from af-Sayyariy from Yahya ibn abu Rafi’ and other in a marfu‘ manner has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘No other food from lunch remains inside until night except bread of rice.’” "
        ]
      }
